# ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
# ║           Market Digest — Environment Configuration         ║
# ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝
#
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your keys:
#   cp .env.example .env
#
# Or run the interactive setup script:
#   ./setup.sh           (macOS / Linux)
#   .\setup.bat          (Windows)
#
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# REQUIRED — Telegram delivery (without these, use --dry-run)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Create a bot via @BotFather on Telegram, paste the token here.
TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=your_bot_token_here
# Your Telegram chat ID (send /start to your bot, then visit
# https://api.telegram.org/bot<TOKEN>/getUpdates to find it).
TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID=your_chat_id_here
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# OPTIONAL — Data sources (enhance digests, but not required)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Without these keys, the system still works using yfinance (free,
# no key needed). Each key unlocks additional data:
# TwelveData — real-time & intraday prices (800 calls/day free)
# Sign up: https://twelvedata.com/pricing
TWELVEDATA_API_KEY=your_twelvedata_key_here
# Finnhub — earnings calendar, economic events (60 calls/min free)
# Sign up: https://finnhub.io/register
FINNHUB_API_KEY=your_finnhub_key_here
# FRED — Federal Reserve economic data (free, unlimited)
# Sign up: https://fred.stlouisfed.org/docs/api/api_key.html
FRED_API_KEY=your_fred_key_here
# NewsAPI — financial news headlines (100 calls/day free)
# Sign up: https://newsapi.org/register
NEWSAPI_KEY=your_newsapi_key_here
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# OPTIONAL — LLM analysis (adds AI commentary to digests)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Without any LLM key, digests run in "facts" mode (data only).
# Add any ONE key to unlock "full" mode (data + AI analysis).
# Priority: Claude → OpenAI → Gemini (uses first available).
# Anthropic Claude — https://console.anthropic.com/
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_anthropic_key_here
# OpenAI — https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_key_here
# Google Gemini — https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
# GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_key_here
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# OPTIONAL — General settings
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Override timezone (default: US/Central)
# TIMEZONE=US/Central
# Log level: DEBUG, INFO, WARNING, ERROR (default: INFO)
# LOG_LEVEL=INFO
